column5: Hey all, looks like it's going to be another grand day.  Enjoy it if you're not working...and do your best to if you are  Maureen
Good morning Mo..  only working half day, but its still work... lol  You have a good day too...
Good mornin' Ladies! It's gonna be very hot and humid here today, perfect for fishin'... but will suck for workin'.
Mornin folks  Sure wish y'all would stop talkin about work, your makin me feel guilty.....  ......well........ maybe not
Bye da lord,it,s a wee bit nipply this morning.LOL  Morn ya,ll.
good morning all,  Is it not a really nice break from the humidity this morning?  Im loving it!  Cheers!
Ya Lew...  Don't they know that "work" is a four-letter word !!!
